---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Trust | Safe DOCX
---
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Trust</p>
  <h1>Read the reliability summary first, then inspect the evidence.</h1>
  <p>
    Built for working developers: quick conclusion first, details after.
  </p>
  <a class="cta" href="traceability/safe-docx/index.html">View Traceability Matrix</a>
</section>

<section class="grid reveal">
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Traceability</h3>
    <p>Every scenario is mapped to concrete test files across both packages.</p>
    <a class="cta" href="traceability/safe-docx/index.html">Safe DOCX</a>
    <a class="cta" href="traceability/docx-core/index.html">DOCX Core</a>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Test Results</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>{{ trustMetrics.allure.results_total_display }}</strong> recorded,
      <strong>{{ trustMetrics.allure.pass_rate }}</strong> pass rate.
    </p>
    {% if trustMetrics.allure.latest_run_utc %}
    <p class="meta">Latest run: {{ trustMetrics.allure.latest_run_utc }}</p>
    {% endif %}
    <a class="cta" href="{{ trustMetrics.reportUrl }}">View full test report</a>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Changelog</h3>
    <p>
      {% if changelog.hasReleases %}
        Latest: <strong>{{ changelog.releases[0].tag }}</strong>
        {% if changelog.releases[0].published_display %}({{ changelog.releases[0].published_display }}){% endif %}
      {% else %}
        Release history auto-generated from GitHub Releases.
      {% endif %}
    </p>
    <a class="cta" href="changelog/index.html">View Changelog</a>
  </article>
</section>
